Arabic numeral to Roman numeral converter program.

Note:
    $PJ_HOME is the directory this readme file is in
    $JNOSS_HOME is the JBoss directory
    
Instructions:
i.    Download and install JBoss 5.1 GA(http://www.jboss.org/jbossas/downloads/)
ii.   Copy sample_build.properties to build.properties and modify it for your environment.
iii.  Copy sample_config.properties to config.properties and modify it to your environment.
iv.   Compile and deploy the application (ant deploy)
        Note - This also restores the DB to a fresh copy.
v.  Start JBoss
vi. Run the program using the client jar. (java -jar IClaudius.jar)

